fs_create_file.examples:
Create a file with content:
```json
{"path": "src/new_module.rs", "content": "//! New module.

pub fn hello() {}
"}
```

Create an empty file:
```json
{"path": "src/placeholder.rs"}
```

resource_links.description:
Links should only contain the path, not the full URL.

Supported formats:
- issue: issues/{number}
- pull: pull/{number}
- commit: commit/{hash}
- file: blob/{hash}/{path}
- lines: blob/{hash}/{path}#L{start}-L{end}

